		"description":{
			"value":"<p><i>A perfectly formed crystal sphere, clutched by three carved dragon claws, tops this handsome mahogany staff.</i></p><p><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Staff</p>\n<p><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p><b>Critical:</b> +2d8 force critical damage</p>\n<p><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain a +2 item bonus to AC.</li>\n<li>You gain a +2 item bonus to skill checks made for performing rituals.</li>\n</ul></p>\n<p><b>Power - At-Will (Minor Action)</b></p><p>Effect: The staff sheds bright light out to 10 squares.</p><p><b>Power - Encounter (Free Action)</b></p><p>Trigger: On your turn, you fail to sustain an arcane implement power you could sustain.</p><p>Effect: You sustain the effect until the end of your next turn. You can still sustain the effect as normal.</p><p><b>Power - Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p>Trigger: You hit an enemy with an arcane implement attack power using this staff and do not score a critical hit.</p><p>Effect: The triggering attack deals maximum damage to one target.</p>",
